<emphasis bold="true" box="[893,920,1911,1933]" pageId="3" pageNumber="288">O)</emphasis>
climbing stem with infructescence and female flowers, 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[136,159,1947,1969]" pageId="3" pageNumber="288">P)</emphasis>
